title: Mkhitaryan
text:
Mkhitaryan, Mkhitarian or Mekhitarian (, <a href="Western%20Armenian">Western Armenian</a> Մխիթարեան) is an <a href="Armenia">Armenian</a> surname. See <a href="wikt%3A%D5%84%D5%AD%D5%AB%D5%A9%D5%A1%D6%80%D5%B5%D5%A1%D5%B6">Մխիթարյան</a> for the origin.
